{"tid":1469534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《機場禁制令應對方法》人手置頂","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:29:25.000Z","uid":3416,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9dcfe71e93293815d79d3ee4ddc0cb62aa3552","tid":1469534,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"機場禁制令係唔比任何人係機管局核准地方以外<br />\n<br />\n進行 示威 抗議 或任何公眾活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">示威 抗議 或公眾活動姐<br />\n<br />\n唔包括係機場行街 自己太攰坐低<br />\n<br />\n咁你拎個空既行李箱去機場 <br />\n痴住文宣係頭<br />\n痴住係個行李箱到<br />\n<br />\n推住架車仔周圍行<br />\n或者太攰坐低係車頭或者地下休息係無問題<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n變番做全和理非回合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">有咩突發情況機管局自然會派人叫你離開<br />\n咁你咪行去T2散下步再黎過囉<br />\n配合番就得<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你係接機大堂萬人接機<br />\n機管局都唔會搞你啦<br />\n宜家係無得封死離境大堂姐<br />\n還原番去和你飛基本步<br />\n<br />\n無需棄餒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家今次可以經一事長一智<br />\n繼續向我地目標努力<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"2f15630cf83aa31ce482343f450c054f235ba381","tid":1469534,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae8fc6615ecb5eaeb23b605aa56c686ff78db58","tid":1469534,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"自推 10連 希望大家唔好小小事就放棄"},{"pid":"21fe85ce2568b2a6cf41564148c9890a35a582d7","tid":1469534,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"ecefd19aef8df22d9a1297b10da1c03e872d8303","tid":1469534,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"自推 10連 希望大家唔好小小事就放棄"},{"pid":"36932763854e7b986d0c20f4f03f3c98e0d0ae71","tid":1469534,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b9ffa8be43a067eb257eb46edb42441912abe4bd","tid":1469534,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"a93bc3d0b925921f93d74f63f1b731ca283897e5","tid":1469534,"uid":75398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅前線們，橫眉冷對千夫指，俯首甘為孺子牛。從來只有暴政，沒有暴徒，感謝勇武前線日以繼夜以命相博 ，方令暴政黑警不致對我們任意妄為，勇武派願意為我們擋子彈，那現在勇武派面臨巨大的輿論壓力，你們會為他們擋嗎？"},{"pid":"9c559d62ee9d7c26f17b88bb3c0fe8571fb698dd","tid":1469534,"uid":290973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a9dcfe71e93293815d79d3ee4ddc0cb62aa3552","tid":1469534,"uid":3416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"機場禁制令係唔比任何人係機管局核准地方以外<br />\n<br />\n進行 示威 抗議 或任何公眾活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">示威 抗議 或公眾活動姐<br />\n<br />\n唔包括係機場行街 自